---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Share a MOment"
  description="Got a photo, clip, or story that belongs in the MOmery archive? Drop it in our shared Google Drive folder, then tell us about it below."
>
  <section class="pt-10 pb-20 px-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-forest text-cream text-center">
    <p class="eyebrow block mb-3">Add to the Archive</p>
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-6">Share a MOment</h1>
    <p class="opacity-80 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10">
      Got a photo, a clip, or a story that belongs here? Drop it right into our shared Google
      Drive folder — anyone with the link can add files directly, no account or sign-up needed
      on our end.
    </p>
    <a
      href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1bPwOQ_GLn0-E2XpyDw37L8LP9cMn67H3?usp=drive_link"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-gold text-forest-deep font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-gold-soft transition-colors"
    >
      Open the MOmery Drive Folder
    </a>
    <p class="opacity-70 text-sm mt-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
      One tip: if you can, name your file with a little context before uploading — something
      like <code class="text-gold-soft">1998_Mary_lake_dock.jpg</code> — so we know who, what,
      and when when it's time to add it to the archive. A note in the file's description works
      too, if your device supports that.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl mt-16 mb-4">Tell us about it</h2>
    <p class="opacity-80 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8">
      Already uploaded a photo or clip? Tell us the story behind it below &mdash; or just
      answer a few questions even if you don't have a file to add.
    </p>
    <div class="momery-form-wrap">
      <iframe
        src="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1M6_1RHz6CDTKfyOY_t2yKk7iBt1eZCUznjZGpp4rcxU/viewform?embedded=true"
        width="100%"
        height="1200"
        frameborder="0"
        marginheight="0"
        marginwidth="0"
      >
        Loading…
      </iframe>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .momery-form-wrap {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #fff;
  }
  .momery-form-wrap iframe {
    display: block;
    border: none;
  }
</style>
